column10: dig_threshold_desc:Nearly every planet I used a strategy of 20+ gems. So when I dug and received somewhere in the twenties
column11: I flew away the next chance I had.
column15: dynamic_desc:I generally knew that if the first dig was 40-50 more than the second dig that I would be leaving the planet after the third dig. If the second dig was only 10-15 lower then I knew I'd be staying longer.
column17: other_desc:Once in a while I chose to dig gems all the way down to a miniscule number somewhere below ten. I tried this in an attempt to see if numbers ever went back up once they reached a certain floor.
column18: feedback:Nothing other than what I've provided above.}
